5
00:02:03,959 --> 00:02:04,980
Grandma Jin...

6
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,659
Her mind is a bit broken.

7
00:02:06,799 --> 00:02:08,379
She just presses it for fun.

8
00:02:08,439 --> 00:02:09,479
Let me tell you,

9
00:02:09,659 --> 00:02:10,860
just this morning,

10
00:02:10,939 --> 00:02:12,900
