11
00:02:14,439 --> 00:02:15,699
She's almost a hundred years old.

12
00:02:15,740 --> 00:02:16,939
Just like a child.

13
00:02:17,060 --> 00:02:19,080
When kids see things that make noise,

14
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,219
