15
00:02:22,860 --> 00:02:23,719
Alright.

16
00:02:24,020 --> 00:02:25,000
I'll go instead.

17
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:25,939
No need to go.

18
00:02:25,979 --> 00:02:27,599
