20
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,139
What problem?

21
00:02:30,259 --> 00:02:32,900
Just those stories from Grandma Jin's past.

22
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:33,580
What?

23
00:02:33,659 --> 00:02:37,000
She's the Ninth Gege of the Aisin Gioro family.

24
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:38,800
A close relative of the Emperor.

25
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:40,000
*My Fair Princess*,

26
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,879
