31
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:49,919
No.

32
00:02:49,979 --> 00:02:51,259
The old lady told me

33
00:02:51,379 --> 00:02:53,080
Jinsuo was based on her.

34
00:02:54,099 --> 00:02:57,159
Maybe Rong Momo was based on her.

35
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:59,039
